description:
Knife Fight - Season 1, Episode 3




Kobayashi vs. Arrington

Elijah Wood and Krista Simmons judges as Nyesha Arrington takes on James Beard nominee Chris Kobayashi in a battle of Hawaiian Kampachi and braised lamb neck. Will this one be too close to call?




Knife Fight - Season 1, Episode 4




Neroni vs. Toft

Two of the hottest new chefs face off as Eater Chef of the Year Jason Neroni takes on Aussie Jordan Toft in a battle of big-eye tuna! Will Jason's last-minute handmade pasta deliver him the big win? Guests include Patrick Fugit.




Original Air Date: 01-Oct-2013
